<div id="review_1243286662" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1243286662" />
    <a title="Ben Loory" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/171197-ben-loory"><img alt="Ben Loory" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1492548411p2/171197.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1243286662?book_show_action=true">Apr 01, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ben Loory" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ben Loory" href="/user/show/171197-ben-loory">Ben Loory</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1243286662" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2227365906102541596">the more pynchon i read the less i understand why anyone gives a shit about pynchon. unfunny, unoriginal, emotionally void, completely lacking in mystery, suspense, or wonder. just a bunch of &quot;wacky&quot; characters talkin &quot;wacky&quot; for 400 pages. like the worst of tarantino, minus the violence and sense of danger.</span>
  <span id="freeText2227365906102541596" style="display:none">the more pynchon i read the less i understand why anyone gives a shit about pynchon. unfunny, unoriginal, emotionally void, completely lacking in mystery, suspense, or wonder. just a bunch of "wacky" characters talkin "wacky" for 400 pages. like the worst of tarantino, minus the violence and sense of danger.</span>
