<div id="review_3778101614" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3778101614" />
    <a title="Vince" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/128225739-vince"><img alt="Vince" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1629724401p2/128225739.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3778101614?book_show_action=true">Jan 17, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Vince" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Vince" href="/user/show/128225739-vince">Vince</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3778101614" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10404572342107341107">One of the easier and more straightforward of Thomas Pynchon&apos;s works with still a lot of psychedelic imagery. Not a favorite like &quot;Gravity&apos;s Rainbow&quot; or &quot;Mason and Dixon&quot; but still a fun and wacky read.</span>
  <span id="freeText10404572342107341107" style="display:none">One of the easier and more straightforward of Thomas Pynchon's works with still a lot of psychedelic imagery. Not a favorite like "Gravity's Rainbow" or "Mason and Dixon" but still a fun and wacky read.</span>
